::DarkMouse::

She had a flood of memories invade her mind. The visions all swirled 
around her.  She saw friends and foe alike around her. It was almost 
too much to take at once.  She cried out in her mind.
She saw visions and memoried that had been long forgotten and not 
wanting to remember them.  She felt like she was drowning.
She wanted it to stop, but the visions and memories just kept 
reaching out to her.
